"title": "5481: proverb",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5481",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A popular saying, regarded as conveying wisdom. Scripture records a great number of didactic proverbs and also preserves some popular sayings.</p>\n<h2>Proverbs identified with wisdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:7\">PRO 26:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:1-Ps49:4\">PSA 49:1–49:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:1-Prov1:6\">PRO 1:1–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:9\">PRO 26:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:9-Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:9–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's many proverbs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29-1Kgs4:34\">1KI 4:29–4:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:1\">PRO 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1\">PRO 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:1\">PRO 25:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:9-Eccl12:10\">ECC 12:9–12:10</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of proverb</h2>\n<h3>On wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">PRO 15:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:13\">PRO 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:2\">PRO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:8\">PRO 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:10\">PRO 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:8\">PRO 14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">PRO 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:4\">PRO 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:8\">PRO 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:30\">PRO 21:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:4\">PRO 23:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:9\">PRO 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:26\">PRO 28:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></p>\n<h3>On righteousness and wickedness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:3\">PRO 10:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:28-Prov10:32\">PRO 10:28–10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:10\">PRO 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:3\">PRO 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:10\">PRO 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:21\">PRO 12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:26\">PRO 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:9\">PRO 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:32\">PRO 14:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:31\">PRO 16:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:15\">PRO 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:26\">PRO 25:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:2\">PRO 29:2</a></p>\n<h3>On wealth and poverty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:22\">PRO 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">PRO 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16\">PRO 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1-Prov22:2\">PRO 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">PRO 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:4-Prov23:5\">PRO 23:4–23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:6\">PRO 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">PRO 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:3\">PRO 29:3</a></p>\n<h3>On speech and silence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:19\">PRO 10:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:12\">PRO 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:18-Prov12:19\">PRO 12:18–12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:20\">PRO 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:28\">PRO 17:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:21\">PRO 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:6\">PRO 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:23\">PRO 21:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:15\">PRO 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:23\">PRO 28:23</a></p>\n<h3>Longer discourses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10-Prov1:19\">PRO 1:10–1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:1-Prov3:10\">PRO 3:1–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:18\">PRO 3:13–3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:1-Prov5:23\">PRO 5:1–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:1-Prov7:5\">PRO 7:1–7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:15-Prov30:16\">PRO 30:15–30:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:21-Prov30:31\">PRO 30:21–30:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10-Prov31:31\">PRO 31:10–31:31</a></p>\n<h3>Popular sayings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:12-1Sam24:13\">1SA 24:12–24:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:9-1Sam10:12\">1SA 10:9–10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:23-1Sam19:24\">1SA 19:23–19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:21-Ezek12:25\">EZK 12:21–12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:44-Ezek16:48\">EZK 16:44–16:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:1-Ezek18:4\">EZK 18:1–18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:23-Luke4:30\">LUK 4:23–4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17-2Pet2:22\">2PE 2:17–2:22</a></p>",
